<p>Mr. BECK. I object to the adoption of that resolution at this time, but I do not object to its reference.</p>
<p>Mr. POTTER. I suggest that the resolution be referred to the Committee on the Judiciary. They have already before them the same subject under a previous resolution of the House.</p>
